Program: Outlook
Title: Sent to War Aged Six
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0358704
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 23 Oct 2015
Deng Adut was raised in war torn Sudan. By the time he was 11 years old, he had been shot, blown up, and was near death from starvation but has now rebuilt his life to become a lawyer in Australia. (Picture: Deng Adut)